The paper deals with echo cancellation, which is a signal processing problem. Therefore, cs.SD (Signal Processing) is the most likely category. The paper also involves adaptive learning, which falls under the umbrella of information theory, making cs.IT (Information Theory) a likely category as well. The proposed method involves closed-loop control, which is a common theme in control systems, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) another possible category. The paper also involves optimization and estimation, which are common topics in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves the use of algorithms and data structures, which are common topics in computer science, making cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) a possible category as well.
